room_title: Escape room "Espionage" by Escape Hotel in Los Angeles
room_description:
Welcome to the military prison. You are being detained for espionage. You can keep your claims of innocence to yourself because nobody here cares. You may be thinking about escaping. Well, you’ll have to think and act like a spy to get out of this room and escape what’s beyond it. But you’ll need to be quick about it…
In just one hour you will be transferred to maximum-security prison and I’ve heard that the other prisoners don’t take kindly to traitors.
